             was indicted for <rs id="t18050424-20-off113" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18050424-20-off113" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050424-20-off113" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050424-20-cd114" type="crimeDate">19th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050424-20-off113 t18050424-20-cd114"></join>, a cloak, value 10 s. a petticoat, value 4 s. three shifts, value 5 s. a sheet, value 4 s. and a pair of stockings, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050424-20-victim252" type="victimName">
                     Charlotte 
                     Mordaunt
                  <interp inst="t18050424-20-victim252" type="surname" value="Mordaunt"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050424-20-victim252" type="given" value="Charlotte"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050424-20-victim252" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
